FBIS4-2719 "drchi071_p_94008" FBIS-CHI-94-071 Daily Report 2 Apr 1994 Central-South Region Hunan Secretary, Governor at University Ceremony Hunan Secretary, Governor at University Ceremony HK1304013394 Changsha Hunan People's Radio Network in Mandarin 2300 GMT 2 Apr 94 HK1304013394 Changsha Hunan People's Radio Network Mandarin BFN [Excerpts] The Hunan Agricultural University solemnly held a renaming ceremony and observed the 43th anniversary of its founding on 2 April. [passage omitted] Present at the ceremony were provincial party and government leaders, including Wang Maolin, Chen Bangzhu, Yang Zhengwu, Hu Biao, Wang Keying, and (Huang Daoqi), (Yang Zhangmin), and other veteran comrades. (Wen Hui), deputy secretary general of the provincial government, read out the State Education Commission's notice of endorsement on renaming the Hunan Agricultural College the Hunan Agricultural University. [passage omitted] On behalf of the provincial government, Vice Governor Wang Keying delivered an ebullient speech. [passage omitted] Amid warm applause Wang Maolin and Chen Bangzhu handed the nameplate of the Hunan Agricultural University to President (Peng Ganzhi). [passage omitted]
